{"tid":498619,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"長澤正美主演月九劇  古澤良太編劇","createTime":"2017-12-14T03:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T08:49:54.000Z","uid":50139,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"68c43c6133a637898a42f3efda83226d6a9b9a09","tid":498619,"uid":50139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"長澤正美暌違十一年主演月九劇古澤良太腳本2018年春播出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/110959_672678b786590a181e50e3aeff116b1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F110959_672678b786590a181e50e3aeff116b1a.jpg&h=cf926ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【劇名】：「the confidence man JP」<br />\n【主演】：長澤正美<br />\n【共演】：東出昌大，小日向文世<br />\n【腳本】：古澤良太（legal high1,2）<br />\n【導演】：田中亮，金井纮<br />\n【官網】：HTTP：//<a href=\"http://www.fujitv.co.jp/confidenceman_jp/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fujitv.co.jp%2Fconfidenceman_jp%2Findex.html&d=oX%2FzVSq82eT82GbXMN2w9FzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=b32b00b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.fujitv.co.jp/confidenceman_jp/index.html</a><br />\n【檔案】：富士台2018年春（4月期）月（星期一）九（晚21:00）<br />\n【劇情簡介】：<br />\n&nbsp;是一部以描繪&ldquo;欺詐遊戲&rdquo;為題材的原創作品。該劇的主題為&ldquo;慾望&rdquo;和&ldquo;金錢&rdquo;，長澤在劇中飾演年齡不詳，身份不明，擁有天才般的知識和超群的集中力，領導般存在的女性欺詐師達子，她和東出昌大（29）飾演的欺詐師博庫及小日向文世（63）飾演的欺詐師理查一起為了異想天開的計劃向佈滿慾望的人們進行金額詐騙。該劇每回以各種華麗的行業為舞台進行描繪，是一部痛快的喜劇作品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【制作班底】：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/111206_291e3a34f5fa677927a4649817e4b8c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F111206_291e3a34f5fa677927a4649817e4b8c9.png&h=944631d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/111221_1556fcd35d24e85157638af0f21054b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F111221_1556fcd35d24e85157638af0f21054b7.jpg&h=4fbee1a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f08e0f2cffaef0a3e5874ba731c7edb77e93f46f","tid":498619,"uid":6310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T03:27:13.000Z","msg":"正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f5dd85994ed8d4091762bc225da72a541fd893","tid":498619,"uid":50139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T03:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb07de162ca56c232d97d7d57b34da07e6bdad1","tid":498619,"uid":49392,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:10:30.000Z","msg":"佢同結衣都似傻西，演醒目角色唔夠說服力"},{"pid":"771c45a26a30ad09c3b9db9c1108de829c8c9f1e","tid":498619,"uid":50139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢同結衣都似傻西，演醒目角色唔夠說服力</blockquote><br />\n都未演過，你又知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795b39720750b0377ff1062509b221c68e18de89","tid":498619,"uid":91527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"咁咪似女版詐欺獵人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b520b6547bbb27582e5ea2fa299240a5585769e","tid":498619,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢同結衣都似傻西，演醒目角色唔夠說服力</blockquote><br />\n都未演過，你又知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢演開傻西嘛，之前有套劇做索腿女警拍到兩輯"},{"pid":"a73dcac3c431f383350bff8d8066dffe4a2281cb","tid":498619,"uid":50139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢同結衣都似傻西，演醒目角色唔夠說服力</blockquote><br />\n都未演過，你又知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢演開傻西嘛，之前有套劇做索腿女警拍到兩輯</blockquote><br />\n所以咪轉緊形囉<br />\n由演學生妹到演傻妹<br />\n近年又拍海街日